    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been such a joy to own\u2014it\u2019s in great shape and drives like a dream! It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, making it the perfect choice if you want something solid and dependable without paying those sky-high dealership prices. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out and come take it for a spin!",
