    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed manual gearbox. The vehicle has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing and reliability. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings, complementing the factory variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. While the exterior reflects its history as a spirited road car, the mechanical vitals\u2014including a recent valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection\u2014confirm a robust powertrain ready for the redline. It offers a tactile, analog steering feel and linear power delivery that defines the golden era of M-division engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
