    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between daily reliability and premium performance. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with only minor road peppering and faint surface marks consistent with careful, regular use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple with minimal bolstering wear, and every interior component\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is robust and turn-key, having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and full fluid service. It tracks straight, shifts with precision, and offers a responsive driving experience that reflects its documented service history. This is a transparent, well-cared-for example ideal for a buyer who appreciates a car that has been respected throughout its ownership.",
