    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend trips. It runs great and is just waiting for a new home! I\u2019m happy to answer any questions you have, so feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
