    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The engine exhibits strong compression and has undergone a recent double-VANOS overhaul and valve shim adjustment to maintain its 8,000 RPM redline integrity. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to address common floor pan fatigue and an M-Variable Differential Lock that provides exceptional mechanical traction. Suspension kinematics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, ensuring the car retains its legendary turn-in precision. This is a mechanically robust 'driver-quality' vehicle with a documented service history, ready for the technical B-roads.",
